snippet.title: USURPER: Soulbound - Trailer
snippet.description:
WISH LIST ON STEAM NOW
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1420510/Usurper/?beta=1

Usurper is a Rogue-lite with Souls-like combat where players are trapped without a physical body in a horrifying dimension and must possess the bodies of their enemies and other heros alike as they fight their way back.
